item.title: CVE-2022-43665|2024-07-31T20:12:45.504Z -- estsoft -- alyac
item.description: A denial of service vulnerability exists in the malware scan functionality of ESTsoft Alyac 2.5.8.645. A specially-crafted PE file can lead to killing target process. An attacker can provide a malicious file to trigger this vulnerability.
